# Inference reads model.pkl, feature_cols.pkl, median_vals.pkl.
# Endpoints read metrics.json, calibration_buckets.json, feature_importance.json.
# Drop the big eval artifacts (PNGs, oof_predictions, xgboost_model.pkl duplicate).
